Task B: Implement product model
Task C: Design authentication flow
```

‚ùå **Sequential** (must run in order):
```
Task 1: Create database schema ‚Üí Task 2: Implement models ‚Üí Task 3: Write API endpoints
```

### Marking Tasks Complete

**Only mark complete when:**
- ‚úÖ All tests pass
- ‚úÖ Blind-validator agent confirms compliance with PRD
- ‚úÖ Acceptance criteria met
- ‚úÖ Code is refactored and clean
